Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Presidential election, November 1976
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjn5s
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Nov 1976
Carter wins presidential election November 1976. Breaks Republican stranglehold of rural America. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less